{{Infobox dungeon |name = Slowpoke Well |image = [[File:Slowpoke Well.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Slowpoke Well. |tokens = 3,500 |location = In Azalea Town. }} '''Slowpoke Well''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Johto]]. It has 36 tiles arranged in a 6x6 square, including 6 chest tiles, 15 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
